On the lateral ankle flap, the Jordan Wings logo is stamped in black, matching the signature Swoosh. Contrasting orange accents land on the padded collar and rubber outsole.

Royal blue accents make their way to the sneaker’s molded eyelets, perforated leather collar and polyurethane midsole, enhanced with visible Air sole cushioning under the heel. The vibrant hue is repeated on Jumpman branding hits at the tongue and back heel.

results.name: Air Force 1 Low GS 'Patriots'
